---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title='Privacy Policy — MFJ Tools'
  description='How MFJ Tools collects, uses, and protects your information.'
>
  <article class='prose max-w-none'>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      This Privacy Policy describes how MFJ Tools (mfjtools.com) collects, uses,
      and protects information when you visit the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Non-personal usage information such as browser type, device, pages
        visited, and approximate location (country/region level).
      </li>
      <li>
        Personal information only if you choose to email us via the contact
        page.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Calculator Inputs</h2>
    <p>
      The numbers you enter into our calculators are processed in your browser
      and are <strong>not</strong> sent to our servers or stored anywhere. We
      have no record of your income, deductions, or any other tax information
      you enter.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We may use privacy-respecting analytics (such as Cloudflare Web Analytics
      or Google Analytics) to understand which calculators are most useful and
      how visitors find the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>
      We use Google AdSense to display ads. Google may use cookies or similar
      technologies to serve ads based on your visits to this and other sites.
      You can learn more or opt out at
      <a href='https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>
        Google's Ads Policy page
      </a>
      or
      <a href='https://www.aboutads.info/choices' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>
        aboutads.info/choices
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you click and make a
      purchase or sign up for a service, we may receive a small commission at no
      extra cost to you. This does not influence our calculator results or which
      tools we recommend.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <p>
      You can disable cookies in your browser settings or opt out of personalized
      ads using the links above.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy? Email
      <a href='mailto:44bsoftware@gmail.com'>44bsoftware@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
